      <description>&lt;DIV&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P&gt;One more thought...&amp;nbsp; here's the link from Allah's site on the item:&lt;/P&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P&gt;&lt;A href="http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/item.html?item=23234" target=_blank&gt;http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/item.html?item=23234&lt;/A&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P&gt;As shown on that site, as you do more LDoN missions (or get more info from the Brotherhood, not sure of the specifics, haven't done that myself yet) there are some stats that grown on this item.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; However, the item is actually used as a transport between camps, and from the Guild Lobby.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &lt;/P&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P&gt;IMO, it's just a must have - takes 5 minutes of your time, and is available to use when you need it.&lt;/P&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P&gt;I was travelling to Iceclad Ocean quite a bit for a while, which usually meant PoK - Freeport West - Freeport East - North Ro - transporter is on the dock.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &lt;/P&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P&gt;Using the Stone, I can just go to Guild Lobby and use the Magus to get to the North Ro camp.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; Then walk over to the transporter.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; Hey, it saves 5 minutes if nothing else.&lt;/P&gt;</description>
